high_descs: Turn left and go to the front of the toilet in the right corner.
Pick up the candle on the top of the tank on the left side.
Turn right and go to the right cabinet below the sink on the left.
Place the candle in the cabinet on the right front side of the soap bottle.
Turn right and go to the bath tub.
Pick up the candle on the left edge of the bath tub in front of the soap bottle.
Turn around and go back to the right cabinet under the sink.
Place the candle on the left of the first candle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left walk towards toilet, turn right walk to toilet
Take candle from the toilet tank
Turn right, walk towards tub, turn left
Put candle in cabinet under sink
Turn right, walk to tub
Get candle from tub ledge
Turn around towards sink
Put candle in cabinet under sink
anns.task_desc: Retrieve two candles in bathroom and put in cabinet under sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the toilet and face it.
Pick up the candle from the toilet lid.
Turn left to approach the sink and face it.
Place the candle in the cabinet under the sink.
Turn right and walk to the tub.
Pick up the candle from the tub.
Turn left to approach the sink.
Place the candle in the cabinet under the sink and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Grab two candles from the toilet lid and bath tub to be placed under the sink cabinet.
